    ("AP_HC","Indian_Polity","Who was the President of the Constituent Assembly of India?","Dr. B.R. Ambedkar","Jawaharlal Nehru","Dr. Rajendra Prasad","Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel","C","Easy","Dr. Rajendra Prasad was elected President of the Constituent Assembly. Dr. Ambedkar chaired the Drafting Committee."),
